@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using BusStationCRM.BLL.Models
@inject SignInManager<User> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<User> UserManager
<div class="dropdown">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        var userInfo = UserManager.FindByNameAsync(User.Identity.Name).Result;
        <button class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="dropdown">
            @userInfo.FirstName @userInfo.LastName
            <span class="caret"></span>
        </button>
        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Tickets" asp-action="Index">My tickets</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Orders" asp-action="Index"> My orders</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" title="Manage">Settings</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <form class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action("Index", "Home", new { area = "" })">
                    <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark">Logout</button>
                </form>
            </li>
        </ul>
    }
    else
    {
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register">Register</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login">Login</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    }
</div>
